{
  "text": "We assessed discrimination of the ordinal logistic model in the same way as a traditional logistic model, using area under the receiver operating characteristic curve [CITATION_1] . We fitted three different models but there was no difference in discrimination between them (area under the receiver operating characteristic curve = 0.755).",
